    +47-930-22764               +47-930-22851




@{b}
Final word
----------
@{ub}
  On behalf of the SilverHawk Software Norway team, I hereby close the
Interplay Project as is without further notice. All I can say is that 
we're sorry we didn't find time to release V5. This was meant to be
the last version. A version with no new special features but with all bugs 
removed and the new GUI added. It would have made a nice xmas present to
al you CDRom users, don't you think ?.    

  
@{b}
To companies
------------
@{ub}
  If your company would like to bundle versions of "CD Player" or "Interplay"
you must contact both of us for an agreement. This also goes to all magazines
who include software on their cover disks/cd's without permission.









@{b}
Yours Sincerely

Espen Skog. 
On behalf of SilverHawk Software Norway
